column1: * In the event a payer has a per hour reimbursement rate, only reimbursement for one hour is represented herein.
* The ER rates herein do not contemplate imaging reimbursement, in the event a contract pays in addition for those services.

* The charges for listed service packages represent median levels on a case basis as experienced at the JV facilities due to the bundled nature of the services. In the event a service package has an insignificant historical volume, no charge will be shown. In these cases, any payer that reimburses on a percent of charge basis will show a reimbursement amount of $0.

* Service package reimbursement for contracts using a percent of traditional Medicare, Medicaid, or Tricare structure rely on the median payment levels on a case basis as experienced at the JV facilities for the traditional referenced payer for that particular service. In the event one of those traditional payers has insignificant volume for a service package, any managed care payer that reimburses on a percent of the traditional payer will show a reimbursement amount of $0.
* Cigna Healthspring rates do not apply to Mansfield and Rockwell locations at time of publishing.
